result.title: My first blog. Some personal feeling. The First time became C.M
result.content:
For a long time, I'd thinked that C.M is the goal of my efforts. But now, it's only the beginning of my next efforts. Nothing're called The End. It's just a new beginning. But, after be C.M, I realy do not know what to do next?!?! Hope after tomorrow contest, I'll know what to do.

It just some words of a newbie's feeling, no think useful, just like a Facebook status, but, hope other newbie may share this feeling with me. Sorry for my bad English.
